data.description: Prime development property at the southwest corner of Ten Mile and Lake Hazel.? Value is in the land and potential re-zoning for greater density (highest and best use), and annexation by City of Kuna to utilize city services stubbed and ready for hookup via Ten Mile.? Round-about being installed by ACHD in near time horizon, 1-2 years.?  Very busy SW corner lot intersection with easy access to Meridian, Nampa and I-84 Ten Mile Interchange.? Property includes a 3 bed 2 bath 2030 sq ft home that is currently on its own well & septic.? Seller is encouraging all offers.
